result.name: Golden Thai Food

reviews.text:
We had lunch there and it is great value. The food is good with only around $50 per head 
I would recommend you arrive by 12:45pm as it will need to queue up at around 1pm

It's Thai cuisine, seems very genuine Thai. In dinner time, it is not easy to get seats. Better come around 6 pm. There are many choices of pork, beef, fish, chicken, curry, noodle and many Veges. Whatever you choose, it must be good one enough. After meal, they provide a simple Thai dessert. Restaurant is clean and the staffs are fairly good.
Food taste good and super speedy service! It just take 5-10mins to wait for the food come! Price is also not expensive and portion is quite big
Very tasty and with good price! Highly recommended !
decent Thai food for a fair price
